Pick all your ideas together and create a clear mind map. Visual diagrams will help you keep in mind any flow of information! 

DIFFERENT PRE-INSTALLED TYPES OF VISUALIZATION
- One-sided map;
- Tree structured;
- Fish-shaped;
- Sun-shaped.

SMART REPRESENTATION
- Different layout structures vary depending on the purpose;
- 3 elements to work with: arrows, stickers and images;
- Applying images or icons to stickers;
- Opportunity to interconnect stickers.

VISUAL BRAINSTORMING RESULTS
- Instant Saving & Sharing;
- You can also print out your projects.

With user-friendly control and understandable functions of Oh! My Mind Mapping 2 the brainstorming process becomes easy and convenient!

